parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or may deploy with excessive force, causing harm to occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag deploys with excessive force
the airbag does not deploy
the airbag sensor needs to be replaced
the dashboard is damaged
and the airbag is protruding from the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the vehicle may not be able to stop in a timely manner.
symptoms: The vehicle takes a long time to stop
the brakes are slow to respond
and the vehicle slows down to 2-3 miles per hour.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rust and corrosion can lead to structural damage, compromising the safety of the vehicle and its occupants.
symptoms: The vehicle is extensively rusty
and the rust is causing damage to the vehicle's structure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the interior door handles can cause difficulty or impossibility in exiting the vehicle, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door handle breaks or becomes inoperable
the door cannot be locked or unlocked from the inside
the door can only be opened from the outside
and the door handle may make a loud clicking or snapping sound when broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle is unable to stop in time to avoid a collision.
symptoms: The vehicle does not stop when the brake is applied
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
and the vehicle may crash into another vehicle or object.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or jerk violently, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle loses power or stalls
the vehicle jerks or bucks violently
the check engine light or wrench light comes on
the vehicle has difficulty accelerating or shifting into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The throttle body failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating
the check engine light or wrench light comes on
the vehicle has difficulty accelerating or shifting into gear
the throttle body sensor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition coil failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or misfire, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle misfires or stalls
the check engine light comes on
the ignition coil fails or explodes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag sensor illumination can cause the airbag to deploy unnecessarily, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag sensor light comes on
the airbag deploys unnecessarily.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The computer and PCM issues can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's computer or PCM malfunctions
the check engine light or wrench light comes on
the vehicle has difficulty accelerating or shifting into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The key and ignition issues can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park or neutral, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition
the vehicle becomes stuck in park or neutral
the steering wheel locks.
